WEBVTT

00:00:00.649 --> 00:00:03.446
Chris Anderson: Well, hello, Helen.
Very nice to see you.

00:00:03.470 --> 00:00:06.326
CA: You staying well?
Helen Walters: How's it going?

00:00:06.350 --> 00:00:10.340
CA: These are mad, mad,
mad, mad, mad days.

00:00:10.364 --> 00:00:11.777
So many emotions.

00:00:11.801 --> 00:00:14.173
Not all bad, happily,

00:00:14.197 --> 00:00:17.626
but I'm just so aware that,
among the people listening to this,

00:00:17.650 --> 00:00:20.111
some are in really tough times right now.

00:00:20.135 --> 00:00:24.764
I hope this is going to be
a beautiful hour of therapy and help

00:00:24.788 --> 00:00:27.650
in its own way,

00:00:27.674 --> 00:00:32.200
because we have with us
just an extraordinary author,